high_descs: Walk straight and around the counter to the left near the door.
Pick up the teapot from the counter.
Turn left and go around the counter to the sink.
Put the teapot in the sink and rinse it and pick it back up.
Turn around and walk to the fridge, take a right and go to the rack.
Set the teapot on the rack.
anns.task_desc: Wash the teapot and put it back on the rack.

high_descs: Move to the side of the counter closest to the door
Pick up a kettle from the counter
Move to the sink ahead of you around the counter
Clean the kettle at the sink
Move to the wooden shelf to the left of you
Place the kettle on the shelf
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned tea kettle on the wooden shelf.

high_descs: Turn to the right and then the left to go around to the far side of the counter.
Pick up the tea pot on the right side of the counter.
Carry the tea pot and turn left, then right to go around the counter. Go to the sink on the right.
Place the tea pot in the sink and turn the water on. Turn the water off and pick up the tea pot.
Carry the teapot and turn around. Then turn right to find the brown shelf in the corner.
Place the tea pot on the next to bottom shelf.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a tea pot and put it away.
